trans-unit.source: Provides a component editor for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollection"></xref> objects in the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Gir et komponent redigeringsprogram for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollection"> </xref> objekter i den tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor class provides a user interface for editing the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyle> elements of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollection> objects in the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control at design time, under the control of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner> object.
trans-unit.target: Klassen MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor gir et brukergrensesnitt for redigering av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyle>elementer i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollection>objekter i den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontroll på utformingstidspunktet under kontroll av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyle>

trans-unit.source: There is a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollection> associated with each of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelMenuItemStyles%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSelectedStyles%2A> properties of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control.
trans-unit.target: Det er en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollection>tilknyttet hver av de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelMenuItemStyles%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSelectedStyles%2A>egenskapene for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSelectedStyles%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelMenuItemStyles%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollection>

trans-unit.source: These <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollection> objects are used to apply styles to menu items that depend on their level (nesting depth) in the menu structure.
trans-unit.target: Disse <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollection>objektene brukes til å bruke stiler til menyelementer som er avhengige av nivåene (nesting dybde) i menystrukturen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollection>

trans-unit.source: The MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor is invoked, for example, by selecting the ellipsis button (**…**) on the **LevelMenuItemStyles** or **LevelSelectedStyles** row in the **Properties** grid of the visual designer.
trans-unit.target: MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor aktiveres, for eksempel ved å klikke ellipsen (**... **) på den **LevelMenuItemStyles** eller **LevelSelectedStyles** rad i den **Egenskaper** rutenett med den visuelle utformeren.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A> method always returns `false` to indicate that only one object can be selected at a time in the editor.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A>metoden returnerer alltid `false` til å angi at bare ett objekt kan velges om gangen i redigeringsprogrammet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor.CreateCollectionForm%2A> method creates a new form to display and edit the current <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollection>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor.CreateCollectionForm%2A>Metoden oppretter et nytt skjema for å vise og redigere gjeldende <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollection>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor.CreateCollectionForm%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor.CreateInstance%2A> method creates a new instance of the specified collection item type.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor.CreateInstance%2A>metoden oppretter en ny forekomst av den angitte samlingen elementtypen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor.CreateInstance%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor.CreateNewItemTypes%2A> method returns an array of types that the editor can create.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor.CreateNewItemTypes%2A>metoden returnerer en matrise av typene redigeringsprogrammet kan opprette.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor.CreateNewItemTypes%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework internally constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor> class when you select, for example, the ellipsis button (**…**) on the **LevelMenuItemStyles** or **LevelSelectedStyles** row in the **Properties** grid of the visual designer when designing a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control or a control that is derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> class.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework internt bygger en ny forekomst av klassen <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor>Når du velger, for eksempel-knappen (**... **) på den **LevelMenuItemStyles** eller **LevelSelectedStyles** rad i den **Egenskaper** rutenett med den visuelle utformeren når du utformer en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontroll eller en kontroll som er avledet fra <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> of the collection to edit.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Type>i samlingen vil</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether multiple <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyle"></xref> elements can be selected in the editor at one time.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om flere <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyle"> </xref> elementer kan velges i redigeringsprogrammet om gangen.

trans-unit.source: The CanSelectMultipleInstances method always returns `false`; thus, only one <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyle> object can be selected at a time in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CanSelectMultipleInstances returnerer alltid `false`; derfor bare én <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyle>objekt kan velges om gangen i den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyle>

trans-unit.source: Always <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Always <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new form to display and edit the current <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollection"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter et nytt skjema for å vise og redigere gjeldende <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollection"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The CreateCollectionForm method calls the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CollectionEditor.CreateCollectionForm%2A> base method to create the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor> form, and then formats a caption for the form.

trans-unit.source: An instance of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CollectionEditor.CollectionForm> to use as the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En forekomst av den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CollectionEditor.CollectionForm>som skal brukes i <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuItemStyleCollectionEditor"> </xref>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CollectionEditor.CollectionForm>

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the specified collection item type.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny forekomst av den angitte samlingen elementtypen.

trans-unit.source: The CreateInstance method is used to create new <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyle> objects.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CreateInstance brukes til å opprette nye <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyle>objekter.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyle>

trans-unit.source: The CreateInstance calls the <xref:System.Activator.CreateInstance%2A> method to access the activation methods for late-bound support.
trans-unit.target: CreateInstance kall av <xref:System.Activator.CreateInstance%2A>metode for å få tilgang til aktivering-metoder for å støtte for sent bundet.</xref:System.Activator.CreateInstance%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> of item to create.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Type>for elementet til å opprette.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.target: En ny forekomst av den angitte typen <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyle"> </xref>.
